	<div class="question">
		Q: If I am awarded a grant, what will be expected of me?
	</div>
	<div class="answer">
		<strong>A:</strong> 
		All grant recipients will be asked to report back to the Alumni Committee within one year to describe their project outcomes or progress to date. Project questionnaires and profiles of funded and completed projects will be posted at <a href="http://gardenhillfund.org">www.gardenhillfund.org</a>. <br>
		Recipients of Garden Hill Grants ($2,000-$10,000) will also be asked to choose one additional way to share their experience with the Mountain School community. This could include:<br>
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp○		a short feature article for the Mountain School Alumni Newsletter<br>
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp○		a video or documentary <br>
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp○		a presentation or participation in a panel at an Alumni event, or at the Mountain School<br>
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp○		a blog  <br>
		&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp○		other creative ideas are welcomed!
	</div><br>	




